For the purposes of this Chapter: 

Agreement on Agriculture means the AgreementonAgriculture, which is part of the WTOAgreement; 

agricultural goods means those goods referred to in Article 2 of the Agreement onAgriculture; 

export subsidies shall have the meaning assigned to that term in Article 1(e) of the AgreementonAgriculture; 

